            <abstract>
                <p>A. Conan Doyle informs Dr Ernst that he will soon receive proofs of the book and will send the whole set. He also mentions a preface for the book and mentions that the book has been described as 'ce mechant livre' in a Boer paper called 'Petit-Bleu'.</p>
